The results in the present study showed that ADAM11-deficient mice slightly , though not significantly , improved <termsem="GO:0050879"> motor </term> <termsem="GO:0007612"> learning </term> ability during rotating rod performance .
However , the deficit of <termsem="GO:0050879"> motor </term> <termsem="GO:0007612"> learning </term> in ADAM11-deficient mice was not clear in this study .
